snippet.title: League Of Enthusiastic Losers Gameplay (PC Game)
snippet.description:
League of Enthusiastic Losers is an adventure game about caring for yourself and your friends, and about not having to be unhappy, just because you are a loser in the eyes of others.
Support the developer by purchasing the game on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1388650/League_Of_Enthusiastic_Losers/
